---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cancellation Policy - NEIC">
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
      <h1>Cancellation Policy</h1>
      
      <h2>Cancellation Notice Required</h2>
      <p>All account cancellations require thirty (30) days advance notice.</p>
      
      <h2>How to Cancel</h2>
      <p>You may cancel your hosted email account by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Emailing our customer service at <a href="mailto:support@natinternet.com">support@natinternet.com</a></li>
        <li>Calling 1-866-667-9277</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Cancellation Timeline</h2>
      <p>If you cancel your account during a billing month, your account will remain active and be terminated as of your next billing date. You will continue to have access to your email services until that termination date.</p>
      
      <h2>Final Charges</h2>
      <p>You remain liable for all charges accrued until your account is deactivated, including full monthly charges for the month during which you submitted your cancellation notice.</p>
      
      <h2>No Mid-Cycle Refunds</h2>
      <p>We do not provide refunds for mid-cycle or mid-month cancellations. Your service will continue until the end of your current billing period.</p>
      
      <h2>Data Retrieval</h2>
      <p>Please ensure you retrieve any important emails, contacts, or files before your account termination date. After termination, data retrieval may not be possible.</p>
      
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about cancellations, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@natinternet.com">support@natinternet.com</a> or call 1-866-667-9277.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>